bangladesh purchas of wheat confirm trade sourc here confirm earlier tent report that bangladesh had bought 200,000 tonn of option origin feed wheat late last week and over the weekend . they said the continent grain co , of the unit state , won the contract to suppli the wheat from the ec and other part of europ . it will suppli 100,000 tonn at a rate of 96.92 u.s. dlr a tonn as a first consign by april 7. it will suppli the remain 100,000 tonn at a rate of 93.42 dlr by april 16 .